c: 6
v: 46
t: "Yithi kwabo (bangakholwayo): “Khanindixeleleni, ukuba uAllâh Anganihlutha ukuva kwenu nokubona kwenu, Atywine neentliziyo zenu, ngubani (omnye) uthixo ngaphandle koAllâh onokunibuyisela ezo (zinto)?” Uyabona ke ukuba Sizicacisa kanjani na iiVesi (zeThu)? Kodwa ngoko kunjalo bayaphambuka"